che Neuperspektivierung die ost- und westdeutsche Literatur gemeinsam in den Blick.  aThe poetics and politics of the border provide a new scientific perspective and establish a German-German literature of the border.  afunded by Bundesstiftung zur Aufarbeitung der SED-Diktatur  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 02. Mrz 2022) 0aAuthors, Germany20th century. 0aBoundaries in literature. 0aGerman literaturey20th centuryxHistory and criticism. 0aPolitics and literaturezGermanyxHistoryy20th century. 4a20. Jahrhundert. 4aDDR-Literatur. 4aDeutsche Geschichte. 4aDeutsche Teilung. 4aGermanistik. 4aKulturgeschichte. 4aLiteratur. 4aLiteraturgeschichte. 4aLiteraturwissenschaft. 4aZweistaatlichkeit. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / German.2bisacsh  a20th Century.  aCultural History.  aDual Statehood.  aGDR Literature.  aGerman Division.  aGerman History.  aGerman Literature.  aHistory of Literature.  aLiterary Studies.  aLiterature.2 aBundesstiftung zur Aufarbeitung der SED-Diktaturefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2018 Part 2z978311076667708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2018z978311071955008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2018z9783110603255oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2018z9783110603187oZDB-23-DKU40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783839444870zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783839444870423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783839444870/original  a978-3-11-071955-0  DG Plus eBook-Package 2018b2018  a978-3-11-076667-7  DG Plus PP Package 2018 Part 2b2018  aEBA_BACKALL 